-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4837ffb\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-c919a54\" data-id=\"c919a54\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d3fbc67 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d3fbc67\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Financial Services<\/strong><\/p><p>A comprehensive financial services course covering the fundamentals of finance, accounting, and economics.<\/p><p>The financial services industry is one of the biggest and most diverse in the world. The sector encompasses a wide range of businesses and activities, from banking and insurance to investment management and brokerages. Financial services companies offer a wide range of products and services to consumers and businesses, and are a key driver of the economy. They are also vital providers of jobs and sources of investment.<\/p><p>Welcome to the Intro to Financial Services course. We&#8217;ll be covering a wide range of topics including: personal finance, banking, investing, and insurance. You&#8217;ll learn the basics to help you build a strong financial foundation and understand the financial world around you. You can write, share, and pause whenever you like.<\/p><p>Financial services are financial activities involved in the provision of financial services for consumers, businesses, and governments. Financial service providers include credit card issuers (credit card companies), banks, investment banks, insurance companies, accountants (who prepare tax returns), mutual funds, stockbrokers (who help people buy and sell stocks and other securities) and so on.<\/p><p>Financial Services is a global trade that involves the provision of financial products and services, either directly to individuals or to businesses. Its main function is to manage personal finance including savings and investments, loans, mortgages, and insurance.<\/p><p>The purpose of this course is to provide you with a solid foundation in the field of financial services. The goal is for you to gain an understanding about how financial services products are structured, how they work and ultimately how to recommend them to your clients.<\/p><p>Whether you are a business or an individual looking to start up your own financial services business, this course has everything that you need to know to get started.<\/p><p>The Financial Services Course was created to help students get their financial careers started by providing them with a practical and comprehensive overview of the industry that will equip them with the necessary skills to succeed.<\/p><p>The Financial Services Course is a web based course that takes you through the process of financial advice and how to set yourself up in practice as a financial planner. The course is aimed at anyone who wants to work in the area of financial planning, whether that be full time or as a side job.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8f60f13 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"8f60f13\" data-element_t